enerated-apology-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/daedalic-entertainment">Daedalic Entertainment</a>对<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum"><em>《指环王：咕噜》</em></a>发行时的状态做出的道歉据称是人工智能提示的结果。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/alan-wake-2-soundtrack-interview-sam-lake-fried-music-3510619">《心灵杀手 2》的“怪人流行歌曲”的制作过程</a></strong></li></ul><p>五月，这款潜行冒险游戏推出时出现了一系列技术问题，激怒了评论者，并成为社交媒体上嘲笑的对象。</p><p>结果，Daedalic Entertainment 选择取消另一款正在开发的<em>《指环王》</em>游戏，并关闭了制作<em>《指环王：咕噜》的德国工作室。</em></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> 《指环王：咕噜》的几句话<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> “团队<a href="https://t.co/adPamy5EjO">pic.twitter.com/adPamy5EjO</a></p><p> — 指环王：咕噜 (@GollumGame) <a href="https://twitter.com/GollumGame/status/1662124108614717448?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>它还对游戏的“平庸”质量表示歉意，并补充说<em>《指环王：咕噜》</em> “没有达到我们为自己或我们的社区设定的期望”。</p><p>然而，在<a href="https://youtu.be/vszf1mwyAfw">德国游戏网站<em>GameTwo</em>的一份报告</a>中，匿名前 Daedalic Entertainment 员工表示，道歉显然是人工智能生成的。</p><p>具体来说，据称发行商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nacon">Nacon</a>使用 ChatGPT 来向玩家道歉。</p><p>因此，据称 Daedalic Entertainment 在社交媒体上发出道歉之前对道歉一无所知。 </p><figure id="attachment_3511793" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511793" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3511793" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3511793" class="wp-caption-text"> 《指环王：咕噜》 图片来源：Nacon</figcaption></figure><p>虽然 Daedalic Entertainment 和 Nacon 都没有承认<em>GameTwo</em>报告中的内容，但粉丝们在道歉声明发布后立即发现了错误。</p><p>其中，游戏被称为“<em>指环王：咕噜</em>”，而不是“<em>指环王：咕噜</em>”。</p><p> <em>GameTwo</em>还采访了技术总监兼高级开发人员 Paul Schulze，他声称游戏的预算太小了，约为 1300 万英镑（1500 万欧元）。</p><p> “有些人在这款游戏上工作了 10 年、15 年、20 年，他们很优秀，但他们无法创造奇迹，因为他们没有获得资金，”他说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3511797" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511797" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3511797" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-ai-generated-apology-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3511797" class="wp-caption-text"> 《指环王：咕噜》 图片来源：Nacon</figcaption></figure><p> “你不能只是在这样的事情上投入更多的钱，再坚持一年，然后一切都会好起来的。这是不现实的，因为它背后的游戏不支持它。”</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系 Daedalic Entertainment 和 Nacon 征求意见。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em>《使命召唤：现代战争 3</em> 》的《僵尸》中将有多个小队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/heres-your-first-look-at-zombies-in-call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-3511745">应对这个备受珍视的系列所面临的最大威胁</a>。</p><p>据称<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-lord-of-the-rings-gollum-apology-was-allegedly-written-with-ai-3511776">，《指环王：咕噜》的道歉帖子是用人工智能撰写的，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
